<div class="container-fluid pt-100 px-4">
    <h1 class='pb-4'>Our Commitment</h1>
    <h3 class='pb-3'>Environmental sustainability, Social responsibility, Transparent Governance</h3>
    <p class="text-md px-4">
        <strong>Konnex Resources</strong> is committed to being a leader in modern mining practices by making
        environmental stewardship, social responsibility, and transparent governance (ESG) the foundation of
        everything we do. In June 2021, the Company established its ESG & Sustainability Committee. The role of the
        committee is to ensure the practices of Konnex Resources and its parent company, Phoenix Copper Limited, are
        meeting and exceeding the laws and regulations put in place to protect the natural resources and communities
        located in and around its mining operations.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid home-wrapper py-100">
    <div class="container ">
        <div class="row justify-content-evenly">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <p class="text-md mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">“A responsible mining operation has
                    the potential to bring sustainable economic benefits to Mackay. I would love to see local businesses
                    thriving and my kids and their classmates with more opportunities to make high-paying wages in town.
                    I’ve found the leadership at Konnex Resources to be great partners for creating these opportunities
                    while placing the highest importance on protecting the area’s lands, waters, and wildlife.”</p>
                <a class="red-btn" href="#" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Have your say</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 p-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
                <img class="esg-header_img" width="100%" src="/images/Lenie Wilkie headshot.jpg" />
                <h3 class="mb-0 esg-img_title" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Lenie Wilkie</br>ESG
                    Coordinator, Mackay
                    resident</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
