<div class="container-fluid py-100 pr team-container mt-60">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row flex-center calc-left">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <img data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000" class="img-fluid w-100" src="/images/esg.jpeg" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 px-50">
                <h3 class="head-lg text-white" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Environmental Stewardship
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white text-md mt-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Custer County and Lost
                    River Valley residents have a fierce pride in the outstanding beauty of their surroundings. As the
                    Empire Mine and other exploration projects advance in the area, the Konnex team continues to make
                    environmental stewardship our top priority.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 pb-100">
    <p class="text-lg py-4 pl-70 text-darkblue" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">In 2017,
        <strong>Konnex</strong> hired an independent environmental engineering company to conduct baseline studies.
        Since then, the company has tracked and studied a variety of elements of the environment including climate and
        air quality, surface and groundwater hydrology, soil characterization, transportation, water use and treatment,
        plant and wildlife, community and infrastructure planning, and much more. This data has helped Konnex understand
        the existing environmental conditions before the start of mining activities and will continue serving as a guide
        for Konnex’s development plans. It will also serve as a benchmark for reclamation at the end of the mine life.
    </p>
</div>
<div width="100% " class="container-fluid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
    <div>
        <h2 class="mb-3 mx-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Empire Mine Environmental Information
        </h2>
        <h3 class="mb-3 mx-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
            Information based on baseline and socio-economic studies by an independent environmental engineering firm.
        </h3>

    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-center justify-between my-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">
        <div class="card card-water">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center" data-bs-toggle='modal'
                data-bs-target="#water-card">
                <img src='/images/water-xxl.png' width='160px' />
                <h5 class="card-title text-center mt-3">Water</h5>
                <p class="card-text">The mine is a zero-discharge facility located high above the water table, meaning
                    water runoff and pollution are not concerns.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-electricity">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center" data-bs-toggle='modal'
                data-bs-target="#electricity-card">
                <img src='/images/plug-xxl.png' width='160px' />
                <h5 class="card-title text-center mt-3">Electricity</h5>
                <p class="card-text">The Company plans to use the source of power currently on the mountain, which comes
                    predominantly from renewables.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-wildlife">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center flex-wrap" data-bs-toggle='modal'
                data-bs-target="#wildlife-card">
                <img src='/images/pawprint-xxl.png' width='160px' />
                <h5 class="card-title text-center mt-3" font-size="19px">Wildlife and Vegetation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Konnex’s activities are not damaging to local wildlife or plant life and will not
                    affect the biodiversity of the area.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-noise">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center" data-bs-toggle='modal'
                data-bs-target="#noise-card">
                <img src='/images/speaker-xxl.png' width='160px' />
                <h5 class="card-title text-center mt-3">Pollution</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Regulators have strict rules around noise, light and dust pollution. Konnex will be
                    required to prove it will eliminate any impact of the pollutants.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class='container-fluid mt-100 ' width='100%'>
    <h2 class="mb-3 mx-5 ms-50" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Visual Expectations</h2>
    <p class='text-lg mx-5' data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="2000">Expected view of Empire Mine site from three
        different
        perspectives show very little visual impact as a
        result of
        mine activities. </p>
